This is a draft for a new design of opensuse.org. Designe means screendesign & layout as well as navigation and interaction strukkture.

To get further informations visit: http://en.opensuse.org/Boosters_Team/Projects/Integrate_all_Infrastructure_under_one_Umbrella

This is just a Mockup od proof of concept. Please don't use it for production! It contains some CSS 3 code, wich works only on webkit and mozilla.

If you have any questions, send a mail to rlihm@opensuse.org